CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1960, pg. A9 reads: "First Prize - The Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority's table, featuring "Bread Around the World," won first prize at the Brotherhood Food Festival sponsored by the Pittsburgh Council of the National Council of Negro Women. Left to right: Alpharetta C. Calloway, Audremas L. Gillard, chairman, and Evelyn Waters. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Alpharetta C. Calloway, Audremas L. Gillard, and Evelyn Waters, posed behind Alpha Kappa Alpha's "Breads of the World" table, in Penn Sheraton Hotel for Brotherhood Food Festival
